item.title: Ip
item.dc:creator: @breaking_the_bridge breaking the bridge
item.description:
@breaking_the_bridge wrote:

Allow other people to join your server and you also by setting up an account at www.no-ip.com,then adding them to your host list on whatever your server name is called, then it will allow the people on your server to join it and play it. Also, you may need to get Hamachi if you don’t already have it at logmeinhamachi.com, and to download a free version, go under overview on the left side of the screen and click free download. You possibly might need a router also. You can probably find a simple router download at www.google.com
